text.tspan: We need the Father, Son, and the Spirit,
Genuine oneness comes by normal growth
Exit the self, by consecration’s oath,
Into the Father, Son, and the Spirit,
Drop the opinions! God’s expression heed!
Deny the self! Take up the cross indeed!
Be in the Father, Son, and the Spirit,
Christ’s death and resurrection paved the way
Moment by moment, let us choose to stay,
Stay in the Father, Son, and the Spirit!
The Father’s life and nature we express—
Within His glory, oneness we possess—
We’re in the Father, Son, and the Spirit!
